OL,3,CHow doorbell cameras have played a
OL,4,Crole in the General Election
OL,6,FBy James Gray, ITV News Producer
OL,8,FKnock, knock. "Hi, it's David
OL,9,FCameron," is probably a greeting many
OL,10,FBritons wouldn't expect to hear on
OL,11,Ftheir doorstep during the run-up to a
OL,12,FGeneral Election.
OL,14,FThe idea of a former prime minister
OL,15,Fappearing behind your front door may
OL,16,Fseem unlikely, but, with the help of
OL,17,Fdoorbell cameras, this election has
OL,18,Fsomewhat put that idea to bed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
