OL,3,CHow doorbell cameras have played a
OL,4,Crole in the General Election
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Lord David Cameron
OL,7,Fis one of several politicians who have
OL,8,Fin fact been caught on the cameras,
OL,9,Fwhile campaigning for their respective
OL,10,Fparties.
OL,12,FThe resulting footage has been widely
OL,13,Fshared online, although not always to
OL,14,Fthe advantage of those captured on
OL,15,Fvideo.
OL,17,FHere, ITV News explores how doorbell
OL,18,Fcameras have helped to play a role in
OL,19,Fthe election, and pull back the
OL,20,Fcurtain on politicians as they meet
OL,21,Fthe electorate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
