OL,3,CHow doorbell cameras have played a
OL,4,Crole in the General Election
OL,6,FMay surprises voters with 'lovely
OL,7,Fmessage'
OL,9,FIt's not every day that a former prime
OL,10,Fminister goes door knocking, but in
OL,11,Fone constituency that's exactly what
OL,12,Fhappened when footage recently emerged
OL,13,Fof Theresa May canvassing support for
OL,14,Fa local Conservative candidate.
OL,16,FMay, who served as PM between 2016 and
OL,17,F2019, can be seen ringing a doorbell,
OL,18,Fprompting the following response: "We
OL,19,Fcan't answer the door right now, but
OL,20,Fif you'd like to leave a message you
OL,21,Fcan do it now."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
