OL,3,CHow doorbell cameras have played a
OL,4,Crole in the General Election
OL,6,FShe can then be seen introducing
OL,7,Fherself and encouraging support for
OL,8,Fthe Tory hopeful, saying: "As you're
OL,9,Fnot in, I'll pop a leaflet through
OL,10,Fyour door."
OL,12,FThe footage left many voters stunned,
OL,13,Fwith some taking to social media to
OL,14,Fvoice their shock.
OL,16,FOne posted on X: "Say what you like
OL,17,Fabout Britain and it's politics... but
OL,18,Fthere ain't many western democracies
OL,19,Fwhere you'd get a former prime
OL,20,Fminister leaving a lovely little
OL,21,Fmessage on your ring doorbell."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
