OL,4,Crole in the General Election
OL,6,FAnother added: "I don't care about my
OL,7,Fpolitical differences with Theresa May.
OL,9,F"If a former PM of the country goes
OL,10,Fout and knocks doors for candidates of
OL,11,Fher party, that shows a dedication to
OL,12,Fpublic service that transcends party
OL,13,Fpolitics."
OL,15,FMay announced earlier this year that
OL,16,Fshe would not be standing for re-
OL,17,Felection, bringing an end to a 27-year
OL,18,Flong career in politics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
