OL,6,FLord Cameron, who was appointed
OL,7,Fforeign secretary last November, can
OL,8,Fbe seen in the video urging support
OL,9,Ffor the candidate, saying: "We'll be
OL,10,Fleaving one of these (leaflets) in
OL,11,Fyour door.
OL,13,F"Thanks very much, have a good day."
OL,15,FLord Cameron served as PM between 2010
OL,16,Fand 2016, and resigned from office
OL,17,Fafter the result of the 2016 Brexit
OL,18,Freferendum.
