OL,3,CHow doorbell cameras have played a
OL,4,Crole in the General Election
OL,6,FOn the flipside, doorbell cameras have
OL,7,Falso shown in the run-up to this
OL,8,Fyear's election how party candidates
OL,9,Fcan be caught out unwittingly through
OL,10,Ftheir choice of words.
OL,12,FScottish Labour candidate Tauqeer
OL,13,FMalik, for example, was filmed telling
OL,14,Fa resident that his party had
OL,15,Fpreviously backed a Conservative win
OL,16,Fin the constituency he is now standing
OL,17,Fin during the 2019 General Election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
