OL,3,CHow doorbell cameras have played a
OL,4,Crole in the General Election
OL,6,FThe footage, which was obtained by the
OL,7,FPress and Journal, showed Malik saying
OL,8,FLabour "did not bother" attempting to
OL,9,Fwin the seat and were instead "hoping"
OL,10,Fthe area's Tory candidate would win.
OL,12,FMalik can later be seen asking the
OL,13,Fresident to vote Labour on July 4 to
OL,14,Fdeny SNP leader in the House of
OL,15,FCommons Stephen Flynn from winning the
OL,16,Fseat.
OL,18,F"Please as a tactical vote, it's only
OL,19,Fbetween me and SNP," Malik says in the
OL,20,Ffootage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
