OL,6,F"I want to get rid of SNP because we
OL,7,Fare very lucky we didn't get
OL,8,Fseparation from the United Kingdom in
OL,9,F2014. Otherwise we were bankrupt
OL,10,Fwithin five months."
OL,12,FA statement issued on Malik's behalf
OL,13,Fafter the footage was released said:
OL,14,F"This election is about the need for
OL,15,Fchange, from two governments that have
OL,16,Fput their own interests before the
OL,17,Fcitizens of Aberdeen South.
OL,19,F"My focus in the last week of the
OL,20,Fcampaign is about the future not the
OL,21,Fpast.
